sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as User Password Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant Auth as Auth Guard
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open password page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW-->>UI: Render change password form

    User->>UI: Submit current and new password
    UI->>LW: updatePassword()
    LW->>LW: Validate current_password and password rules
    LW->>Auth: Resolve current authenticated user
    Auth-->>LW: Current user
    LW->>DB: Update user password
    DB-->>LW: Password updated
    LW-->>UI: Reset form fields + success toast
